{
  "description": "A picturesque coastal scene featuring waves crashing onto a gray sand beach under a bright blue sky with wispy cirrus clouds. A single bird is soaring in the distance, adding a sense of scale and freedom. The waves vary in size, with some forming white crests as they break. The water transitions in color from a darker teal further out to lighter shades of turquoise and white as it nears the shore. The distant coastline is barely visible, forming a subtle horizon line. The overall composition evokes a feeling of tranquility and natural beauty.",
